<section class="manifesto">
  <div class="glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap manifesto-inner" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center">Our one rule</span>
    <h2>AI <span class="accent">and</span>.<br />Not AI instead.</h2>
    <p>
      AI is additive to craft, not a replacement for it. We use every tool we have to move faster and
      reach further, then put a human on every detail that matters. That is the part you can feel.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-block: clamp(78px, 11vw, 140px);
  }
  .manifesto .glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: min(90vw, 760px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.72 0.06 272 / 0.18), transparent 66%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .manifesto-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .manifesto h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5.2rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 14px 0 0;
  }
  .manifesto p {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.7vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 54ch;
    margin: 22px auto 0;
  }
</style>
